{
  "texts": [
    "The final source contains 7,586 events from 4,153 woman and 3,444 man subjects.",
    "We test the current state-of-the-art LLMs Llama2 (Touvron et al., 2023), GPT-4 (OpenAI, 2023), and Mistral-7b (Jiang et al., 2023).",
    "We examine all versions in the Llama2 family's dialogueoptimized versions: Llama-2-7b-chat-hf, Llama-2-13b-chat-hf, and Llama-2-70b-chat-hf.",
    "We refer to these models throughout the paper as Llama2-7b, Llama2-13b, and Llama2-70b, respectively.",
    "Among the models released by Mistral, we test the instruction-tuned version Mistral-7b-Instruct-v0.1."
  ]
}